This has gotten too wierd for me guys. Is every post going to be an assumption that it is from a troll?  Can't their be a filtering process here?<br>
My favorite president said &quot;Trust - but verify&quot;. Can we do no less?  If someone posts here there is enough time to verify their credentials. And would it be so wrong if we trust someone and later find that they are liars? Isn't it easier to let someone ask their questions, make their comments and then verify?<br>
How many have been turned off or have turned away from this place for fear of an attack?<br>
Can't we extend a hand of friendship and welcome to those who come here?<br>
P.S. You want to verify this is me. Ask!<br>
